# Core platform paths require organiser review; modules/ is deliberately
# UNOWNED so a team PR touching only its own folder merges on green CI with no
# review queue. NOTE: this file only blocks merges if branch protection on main
# has "Require review from Code Owners" enabled — turn that on before event day.
#
# Later match wins, so the core rules come after the (absent) module rule.

